data.description: This Gracepoint Turnkey elegant stone front home features 4 Bedrooms with 3.5 baths move in ready. 3 car tandem garage. High ceilings in the Kitchen and Family room area that leads out to a huge covered patio in your fully fenced backyard.   This home also has a study as you walk in from your covered front porch. Formal dining room is centrally located off the extended foyer. Large breakfast area open to the island kit w/SS Appliances, granite kitchen counter tops & 42'' Maple cabinets. Master bedroom includes a large closet, soaking tub, double sinks and separate shower.  3 secondary bedrooms located upstairs w/spacious game room. Completely gated Full sod, sprinkler system and home alarm. All the amenities you desire are in this community. Call Earl today to schedule your showing!
